name: Winter to summer
description:
Sound ON.
It was a very beginning of my growing as a creator. On video my lovely city Odessa, Ukraine. I came there to study in nautical academy to become a guy, writing this description. Our life it's just changing of seasons. It's not only season of the year, it's seasons of our life. For sure everyone have memories connected with winter. summer, autumn and spring. Whether it's about first love, new job or even big new step in our lives.
Collection "Seaman's life" beginning from this video.
